le\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republican_Front_(France)\", \"score\": 0.8193581853944043, \"rank\": 0.18409090909097742, \"text\": \"Republican front\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republican_Front_(France)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republican_Front_(France)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tactical-voting agreement\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"cordon sanitaire\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday's second round\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the far right\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a danger in France\\\" of a far-right victory so \\\"we need to vote,\\\" one Parisian, Anne Boudin, 58, told NBC News on Sunday as she went to cast her ballot in the contest's second round.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9999378109198539, \"rank\": 6.15933941011652e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1935, \"end\": 1943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9890377433048747, \"rank\": 0.011083759508299606, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a danger\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"a far-right victory\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"one Parisian\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"Anne Boudin\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"her ballot\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"the contest's second round\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2014}]}, {\"sentence\