n\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4765}, {\"ngram\": \"his second and final presidential term\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if he does manage to cobble together a government, it will be hard for Macron to pursue his pro-business agenda.\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4929, \"end\": 4935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8725010792775772e-44, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a government\", \"from\": 4895, \"to\": 4907}, {\"ngram\": \"his pro-business agenda\", \"from\": 4946, \"to\": 4969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Likewise, the leftists with their hopes of raising the minimum wage and freezing energy prices.\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 5066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Likewise, the leftists\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4993}, {\"ngram\": \"their hopes\", \"from\": 4999, \"to\": 5010}, {\"ngram\": \"the minimum wage\", \"from\": 5022, \"to\": 5038}, {\"ngram\": \"energy prices\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the short term, opponents of the far-right are claiming at least some semblance of victory.\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the short term\", \"from\": 5071, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"opponents\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5096}, {\"ngram\": \"the far-right\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5113}, {\"ngram\": \"at least some semblance\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5150}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 5154, \"to\": 5161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But few are kidding themselves that this is the end of the debate.\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5207, \"to\": 5214}, {\"ngram\": \"the debate\", \"fro